### 🗓️ Time Intelligence & Data Modeling (DimDate Dimension)

To support robust time-series analysis and enable advanced **Time Intelligence** calculations in Power BI, a dedicated Calendar Dimension table (`dbo.DimDate`) was engineered. This table spans a historical horizon from **2020-01-01 to 2025-12-31**, breaking down raw dates into analytical attributes such as weeks, quarters, month names, and weekend indicators (`IsWeekend`) for granular filtering.

#### T-SQL Date Dimension Seed Script:
```sql
